{
  "stem": "27509.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And to the extent to which they could help us, or give us some merchandise to go and sell, or to bring, or-- to that extent, people started to just unwind, and do something.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Money exchange was a major business in Shanghai in those days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The exchange shops in Shanghai were something to be seen to be believed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any currency, anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the days before computers, and before-- before-- they had their Chinese abacus-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to sit with two telephones, talking to two different-- listening to two different people from-- and-- and-- and with one hand doing the calculation on the abacus, and dealing straight away with also two people.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a sight to see, because they are-- their agility-- their agility, both in terms of their fingers, and their mind, and their mathematical capacity, was something to be extraordinary.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what was so strange about it is that some Jewish refugees who were smart, and had the knack for these sort of things, started trading outside their shops, next to them-- traded currency.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was legal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You could handle any currency.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You could buy pounds, and dollars, in whatever currency it was, buy and sell.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everything was-- everything was a commodity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In war time, American dollars were certainly a commodity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's for sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was no better commodity than America dollars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people started buying and selling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the market required different things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One day, the market wanted razor blades.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was war time-- war time economy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not that-- there is a demand from the market that the market requires something.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
